          ['Do you provide nursing as well as everyday help?', 'Yes — registered nurses for wound care, medication and health checks, alongside personal care, cleaning, meals and social support.'],
          ['Can services be changed or cancelled later?', 'Yes, any time. There are no lock-in contracts and no exit fees.'],
